cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE. 

This paper is about sentiment analysis on Twitter using deep learning techniques, specifically CNNs and LSTMs. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves training and fine-tuning of neural networks, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of pre-trained word embeddings and distant supervision involves techniques from cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with information retrieval and classification, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
